title: 164: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode (Feb '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode (Feb '22 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang tried a whopping 15 items from TJ’s. There’s meatless meat lover’s pizza, vegan feta, a sriracha shrimp bowl, coffee BBQ sauce, an amazing three layer hummus, a non-dairy frozen dessert cone, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a new salad dressing that you’re going to want to buy ASAP… It’s that good! Push play now, then when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the items mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: It’s that time again, another stellar Trader Joe’s Haul!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
